reception and providing an index of people and works.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aDeutsch / Literatur. 4aExilliteratur. 4aHorváth, Ödön von. 4aTheatergeschichte. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  aGerman / literature.  aHorváth, Ödön von.  aexile literature.  atheater history.1 aBalme, Christopher B., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBartens, Daniela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBertschik, Julia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEnder, Markus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFuchs, Gerhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGartner, Erwin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGruber, Klemens, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHansel, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHanuschek, Sven, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHofeneder, Veronika, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHuber, Mario, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHöfer, Günther A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aInnerhofer, Roland, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKastberger, Klaus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKoberg, Roland, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKrammer, Stefan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMeister, Monika, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMüller-Funk, Wolfgang, econtributor.4ctb4htt